{"tid":2436638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"直擊疫情被捕 方斌失蹤逾年","createTime":"2021-03-07T09:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T09:41:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"afc75b35f102c4462ec882adaee2dea7c6a8fc8d","tid":2436638,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/3D4KSJTKSJDV3MBXSXBJY7EM54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2F3D4KSJTKSJDV3MBXSXBJY7EM54%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bCuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=7d09dd05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2F3D4KSJTKSJDV3MBXSXBJY7EM54%2F&h=eb4cb4cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/3D4KSJTKSJDV3MBXSXBJY7EM54/</a><br />\n<br />\n直擊疫情被捕 方斌失蹤逾年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zc39azf24L3rksi3-C0NpLjYpFo=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCI2SRL6WJBKJBZYPLWVX7CUHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fzc39azf24L3rksi3-C0NpLjYpFo%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCI2SRL6WJBKJBZYPLWVX7CUHA.jpg&h=de50afd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公民記者方斌失蹤一年，至今音訊全無。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐武漢期間，在當地醫院拍攝實況的商人方斌，被當局抓捕後下落不明，至今超過一年。前中共黨校學者蔡霞在Twitter發帖呼籲，不能放棄尋找方斌。至於因尋釁滋事罪被判囚四年的公民記者張展，則在上月透過視像方式與母親會面，據稱她堅持在獄中半絕食。<br />\n<br />\n「一年了，似乎外界得不到任何方斌的消息，令人揪心。」蔡霞在Twitter轉發方斌在武漢的影片，並引用「為眾人抱薪者，不可使其凍斃於風雪；為自由開闢道路者，不可使其困頓於荊棘」，呼籲眾人不能忘記方斌，不能放棄尋找方斌。方斌去年2月武漢疫情爆發期間，到當地多間醫院直擊，曾拍攝一間醫院五分鐘內搬運八具遺體的畫面，引發外界關注。他之後被帶走，一直沒有消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張展堅持半絕食<br />\n<br />\n同樣在武漢當地報道疫情的張展，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter"}]}